{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place parsley and 1 sprig thyme in mixing bowl then chop <b>2 sec\/speed 8<b>. Transfer to a bowl and set aside.","Arrange leeks, cut side up, in Varoma dish and on Varoma tray. Insert Varoma tray into Varoma dish, cover Varoma and set aside.","Make cuts in potatoes, 2-3 mm apart, without cutting all the way through, to create a fan (see tip). Spread rosemary and remaining 2 sprigs thyme between slits and sprinkle lightly with salt","Place water in mixing bowl. Insert simmering basket and place prepared potatoes inside, cut side up. Place covered Varoma into position and steam <b>20 min\/Varoma\/speed 2<b>.","Remove Varoma and set aside. Remove simmering basket with aid of spatula and keep leeks and potatoes warm. Empty mixing bowl, reserving cooking liquid.","Place garlic and onion in mixing bowl then chop <b>5 sec\/speed 5<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula.","Add oil and, without measuring cup, cook <b>3 min\/120°C\/speed 1<b>.","Add mushrooms and, with simmering basket in place of measuring cup, sauté <b>4 min\/120°C\/\/speed 1<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula.","Add wine and reduce <b>1 min\/100°C\/\/speed 1<b>.","Add ⅔ reserved chopped herbs, vegetable stock and 100 g reserved cooking liquid then cook <b>4 min\/100°C\/\/speed 1<b>.","Add soy cream, salt and pepper then mix <b>5 sec\/\/speed 1<b>. Garnish mushroom ragout with remaining chopped herbs and serve with leeks and potatoes."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["2 sprigs fresh flat-leaf parsley, leaves only","3 sprigs fresh thyme, leaves only","500 g leeks, halved lengthways then sliced (5 cm)","4 waxy potatoes, unpeeled, medium (approx. 80 g each)","1 sprig fresh rosemary, leaves only","500 g water","2 garlic cloves","1 red onion (approx. 110 g), quartered","20 g olive oil","400 g fresh mushrooms, mixed (e.g. chanterelles, oyster), cut in pieces (1-2 cm)","50 g white wine, vegan","1 heaped tsp vegetable stock paste, homemade, vegan (see tip)","100 g soy cream, for cooking","¾ tsp fine sea salt, plus extra to taste","½ tsp ground black pepper"]}],"id":"r429886","imageLink":"https:\/\/1.bp.blogspot.com\/-ajLnucYcqp0\/XZVPxW2kXyI\/AAAAAAAAc8Y\/EQw0DtcdGm4av8iDWnRoMFWkdzWV6q-xgCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_Ea3xt7bXWoDD3hSc.png","title":"Mushroom Ragout with Steamed Leeks and Hasselback Potatoes","publishedAt":"2018-12-10T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"9 g","fat":"10 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"20 g","calories":"956 kJ \/ 228 kcal"},"basicInfo":["medium","35m","1h 15m","4 portions"]}